  <li>Schedule a session with Dr. Meaghan Rice or another therapist on our team through the booking link on our site.</li>
  <li>Reach out via our contact form to ask questions or find out if we are a good fit for your family.</li>
</ul>

<p>Your teen does not have to struggle alone, and neither do you. We are here to help.</p>
